outh Korean Gaon Music Chart: Online download (Foreign) \u2013 The 2nd Week of 2016| work=Gaon Music Chart| publisher=Korea Music Content Industry Association| accessdate=January 17, 2016|language= Korean}}\n*{{cite web| url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?serviceGbn=S1020&termGbn=week&hitYear=2016&targetTime=04&nationGbn=E| title=South Korean Gaon Music Chart: Online download (Foreign) \u2013 The 3rd Week of 2016| work=Gaon Music Chart| publisher=Korea Music Content Industry Association| accessdate=January 31, 2016|language= Korean}}\n*{{cite web| url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?serviceGbn=S1020&termGbn=week&hitYear=2016&targetTime=05&nationGbn=E| title=South Korean Gaon Music Chart: Online download (Foreign) \u2013 The 4th Week of 2016| work=Gaon Music Chart| publisher=Korea Music Content Industry Association| accessdate=February 6, 2016|language= Korean}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Spain|certyear=2016|relyear=2015|artist=Ariana Grande|title=Focus|award=Gold|salesamount=20,000|type=single|certref=<ref>{{cite web|accessdate= January 16, 2016 |title= Top 100 Canciones - Semana 01: del 1.1.2016 al 7.1.2016|url= http://www.promusicae.es/listas/semana/3059-canciones-semana-1-2016 |publisher= [[PROMUSICAE]]|format = PDF|language = Spanish}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Sweden|certyear=2016|relyear=2015|artist=Ariana Grande|title=Focus|award=Platinum|type=single|certref=<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sverigetopplistan.se/netdata/ghl002.mbr/artdata?dfom=20160314&sart=6606972|title=Ariana Grande - Focus|publisher=[[Swedish Recording Industry Association|Grammofon Leverant\u00f6rernas F\u00f6rening]]|accessdate=April 6, 2016|language=Swedish}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United Kingdom|certyear=2016|relyear=2015|artist=Ariana Grande|title=Focus|award=Silver|type=single|accessdate=January 29, 2016}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United States|certyear=2016|relyear=2015|artis