>{{cite web|accessdate= January 16, 2016 |title= Top 100 Canciones - Semana 01: del 1.1.2016 al 7.1.2016|url= http://www.promusicae.es/listas/semana/3059-canciones-semana-1-2016 |publisher= [[PROMUSICAE]]|format = PDF|language = Spanish}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Sweden|certyear=2016|relyear=2015|artist=Ariana Grande|title=Focus|award=Platinum|type=single|certref=<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sverigetopplistan.se/netdata/ghl002.mbr/artdata?dfom=20160314&sart=6606972|title=Ariana Grande - Focus|publisher=[[Swedish Recording Industry Association|Grammofon Leverant\u00f6rernas F\u00f6rening]]|accessdate=April 6, 2016|language=Swedish}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United Kingdom|certyear=2016|relyear=2015|artist=Ariana Grande|title=Focus|award=Silver|type=single|accessdate=January 29, 2016}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United States|certyear=2016|relyear=2015|artist=Ariana Grande|title=Focus|award=Platinum{{sup|{{Dagger}}}}|type=single|accessdate=January 27, 2016|salesamount=1,000,000<!--CERTIFICATIONS Don't Mean Sales. Please Don't change Pure Sales figure unless you have a source-->|salesref=<ref name=\"us_sales\">{{cite web|last1=Trust|first1=Gary|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8363518/ariana-grande-career-album-song-sales-ask-billboard|title=Ask Billboard: Ariana Grande's Career Album & Song Sales|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|publisher=([[Prometheus Global Media]])|date=April 22, 2018|accessdate=April 22, 2018}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom|nosales=true|streaming=true}}\n{{small|{{sup|{{Dagger}}}} Since May 2013 RIAA certifications for digital singles include on-demand audio and/or video song streams in addition to downloads.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.riaa.com/newsitem.php?content_selector=riaa-news-gold-and-platinum&news_month_filter=5&news_year_filter=2013&id=C19496E7-CEC0-C453-D8A1-BD80E56E610F |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6hh144TjH?url=http://www.riaa.com/riaa-adds-digital-streams-to-historic-gold-platinum-awards/ |archivedate=2016-05-22 |title=RIAA Adds Digital Streams To Historic Gold & Platinum Awards |publisher=[[Recording Industry Association of America]] |date=May 9, 2013 |accessdate=May 9, 2013 |url-status=dead }}</ref>}}\n\n==Radio and release history==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Region\n! scope=\"col\"| Date\n! scope=\"col\"| Format\n! scope=\"col\"| Label\n! scope=\"col\" | {{Tooltip|Catalog|Catalogue}}\n! scope=\"col\" |{{Tooltip|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | United Kingdom\n| {{start date|2015|10|30}}\n| [[Music download|Digital download]]\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[Republic Records|Republic]]\n| rowspan=\"4\" {{N/A|None}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref name=\"Di\">{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/focus-single/id1053101839|title=Focus \u2013 Single by Ariana Grande|publisher=[[Apple Inc.|Apple]]|work=[[iTunes Store]]|accessdate=October 30, 2015}}</ref> \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | United States\n| {{start date|2015|11|2}}\n| [[Hot adult contemporary]] radio\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allaccess.com/hot-modern-ac/future-releases |title=Hot/Modern/AC > Future Releases |publisher=Allaccess.com |accessdate=October 31, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ch6paQar?url=http://www.allaccess.com/hot-modern-ac/future-releases |archivedate=October 31, 2015 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{start date|2015|11|3}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Contemporary hit radio]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.republicplaybook.com/track/ariana-grande-focus/ |title=Top 40 {{!}} Ariana Grande \"Focus\" {{!}} Republic Playbook |publisher=[[Republic Records]] |accessdate=October 31, 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031151058/http://www.republicplaybook.com/track/ariana-grande-focus/ |archivedate=October 31, 2015 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Italy\n| {{start dat