ukkampetti]]'' || Scariah\n|\n|-\n|181\n| ''[[Kuttapathram]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|182\n| ''[[Eagle (1991 film)|Eagle]]'' || Appukuttan/Murugadas\n|\n|-\n|183\n| ''[[Maydinam]]'' || Ouseph\n|\n|-\n|184\n| ''[[Mimics Parade]]'' || Fr. Tharakkandam\n|\n|-\n|185\n| ''[[Oru Tharam Randu Tharam Moonu Tharam]]'' || Adithya Pilla\n|\n|-\n|186\n| ''[[Pookkalam Varavayi]]'' || Pothuval\n|\n|-\n|187\n| ''[[Sandesam]]'' || Yaswanth Sahai\n|\n|-\n|188\n| ''[[Ulladakkam]]'' || Kunjachan\n|\n|-\n|189\n| ''[[Kizhakkunarum Pakshi]]'' || Girijavallabha Panikkar\n|\n|-\n|190\n| rowspan=\"20\" | 1990|| ''[[Anantha Vruthantham]]'' || Padmanabhan\n|\n|-\n|191\n| ''[[Kalikkalam]]'' || Velayil Chandy\n|\n|-\n|192\n| ''[[Kottayam Kunjachan]]'' || Mikhael\n|\n|-\n|193\n| ''[[No.20 Madras Mail]]'' || Narayanan Nadar\n|\n|-\n|194\n| ''[[Cheriya Lokavum Valiya Manushyarum]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|195\n| ''[[Dr. Pasupathy]]'' || Dr. Pasupathi/Bhairavan\n|\n|-\n|196\n| ''[[Kouthuka Varthakal]]'' || Suryanarayana Iyer\n|\n|-\n|197\n| ''[[Pavakkooth]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|198\n| ''[[Malayogam]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|199\n| ''[[Mukham]]'' || Anthony\n|\n|-\n|200\n| ''[[Nagarangalil Chennu Raparkam]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|201\n| ''[[Ottayal Pattalam]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|202\n| ''[[Gajakesariyogam]]'' || Ayyappan Nair\n|\n|-\n|203\n| ''[[Rajavazhcha]]'' || Ittoopp\n|\n|-\n|204\n| ''[[Saandhram]]'' || Paulo\n|\n|-\n|205\n| ''[[Sasneham]]'' || Eanasu\n|\n|-\n|206\n| ''[[Shubhayathra|Subhayathra]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|207\n| ''Superstar'' || Devasyya\n|\n|-\n|208\n| ''[[Thalayanamanthram]]'' || Daniel\n|\n|-\n|209\n| ''[[Thooval Sparsam]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|210\n| rowspan=\"17\"|1989|| ''[[Swagatham]]'' || Labrador bhai\n|\n|-\n|211\n| ''[[Chakkikotha Chankaran]]'' || Bhagavathar\n|\n|-\n|212\n| ''[[Innale]]'' || Shankara Pillai\n|\n|-\n|213\n| ''[[Jaathakam|Jathakam]]'' || Kunjuraman\n|\n|-\n|214\n| ''[[Kaalal Pada]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|215\n| ''[[Annakutty Kodambakkam Vilikkunnu]]'' || Avarachan\n|\n|-\n|216\n| ''[[Utharam]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|217\n| ''[[Aavanikunnile