hna Ravu\n|\n|-\n|253\n|rowspan=\"34\"| 1986|| ''Ee Kaikalil'' || Ittoopp\n|\n|-\n|254\n| ''Nyayavidhi'' || Channar\n|\n|-\n|255\n| ''Rareeram'' || Lonappan\n|\n|-\n|256\n| ''Ayalvasi Oru Daridravasi'' || Kuttan Pillai\n|\n|-\n|257\n| ''[[Dheem Tharikida Thom]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|258\n| ''[[Ente Sonia]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|259\n| ''[[Oridathu]]'' || Dr Rajasekharan\n|\n|-\n|260\n| ''Ente Entethu Mathram'' ||\n|\n|-\n|261\n| ''Atham Chithira Chothi'' || Mathan\n|\n|-\n|262\n| ''Nilakurinhi Poothappol'' || Kuttan Nair\n|\n|-\n|263\n| ''[[Revathikkoru Pavakkutty]]'' || Bhasi Pillai\n|\n|-\n|264\n| ''[[Ice Cream]]'' || Police Inspector\n|\n|-\n|265\n| ''[[Sanmanassullavarkku Samadhanam]]'' || Kunji Kannan Nair\n|\n|-\n|266\n| ''[[Sunil Vayassu 20]]'' || Anthony\n|\n|-\n|267\n| ''[[Geetham (film)]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|268\n| ''[[Amme Bhagavathi]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|269\n| ''[[Pappan Priyappetta Pappan]]''||\n|\n|-\n|270\n| ''[[Chidambaram (film)]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|271\n| ''[[Koodanayum Kattu]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|272\n| ''[[Prathyekam Sradhikkukka]]'' || Pothachan\n|\n|-\n|273\n| ''Katturumbinum Kaathukuthu'' ||\n|\n|-\n|274\n| ''[[Oru Kadha Oru Nunakkadha]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|275\n| ''Aavanaazhi'' ||\n|\n|-\n|276\n| ''[[Ithile Iniyum Varu]]'' || Dasappan\n|\n|-\n|277\n| ''Naale Njangalude Vivaaham'' ||\n|\n|-\n|278\n| ''Doore Doore Oru Koodu Koottam'' ||\n|\n|-\n|279\n| ''Meenamaasathile Sooryan'' || Adhikari\n|\n|-\n|280\n| ''Mizhineerppoovukal '' ||\n|\n|-\n|281\n| ''Illenjippookkal'' || Kaduvappara Pappu\n|\n|-\n|282\n| ''Vivahitare Itihile'' || Kuriachan\n|\n|-\n|283\n| ''[[Oru Yugasandhya]]'' || Sreedharan Nair\n|\n|-\n|284\n| ''[[Gandhinagar 2nd Street]]'' || Policeman\n|\n|-\n|285\n| ''[[Chilambu]]'' || Enashu\n|\n|-\n|286\n| ''[[Yuvajanotsavam]]'' || Kunjunni Nair\n|\n|-\n|287\n|rowspan=\"17\" | 1985|| ''[[Kandu Kandarinju]]'' || Thomas\n|\n|-\n|288\n| ''[[Kathodu Kathoram]]'' || Kapyar\n|\n|-\n|289\n| ''Ee Lokam Ivide Kure Manushyar'' || Ouseppu\n|\n|-\n|290\n| ''Ayanam'' || Chakkunni\n|\n|-\n|29