hambu Nair\n|\n|-\n|222\n| ''[[Ramji Rao Speaking]]'' || Mannar Mathai\n|\n|-\n|223\n| ''[[Vadakkunokkiyantram]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|224\n| ''[[Antharjanam (film)|Antharjanam]]'' || Vathapally Varkey\n|\n|-\n|225\n| ''[[Varavelpu]]'' || Chathutty\n|\n|-\n|226\n| ''[[Varnam (1989 film)|Varnam]]'' || Bhaskaran Pillai\n|\n|-\n|227\n| rowspan=\"13\"| 1988|| ''[[August 1 (film)|August 1]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|228\n| ''[[Dhwani]]'' || Rappayi\n|\n|-\n|229\n| ''[[Moonnam Mura]]'' || Kisan Jacob\n|\n|-\n|230\n| ''[[Mukunthetta Sumitra Vilikkunnu]]'' || Ramendra\n|\n|-\n|231\n| ''Pattana Pravesham'' || Puthanpurackal Balan\n|\n|-\n|232\n| ''Ponn Muttyidunna Tharavu'' || P.V. Panikkar\n|\n|-\n|233\n| ''Simon Peter Ninakku Vendi'' || Vaniyambadi Chandran\n|\n|-\n|234\n| ''[[Vellanakalude Nadu]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|235\n| ''[[Witness]]'' || Sankunni Nair\n|\n|-\n|236\n| ''[[Aryan (1988 film)|Aryan]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|237\n| ''Puavrutham'' || Kelu Nair\n|\n|-\n|238\n| ''[[Charavalayam]]'' || Kumaran\n|\n|-\n|239\n| ''[[Oru Muthassi Katha]]'' || Thampuran\n|\n|-\n|240\n|rowspan=\"13\"|1987|| ''Ayitham'' || Joseph\n|\n|-\n|241\n| ''[[Thaniyavarthanam]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|242\n| ''[[Sreedharante Onnam Thirumurivu]]'' || Sadasivan\n|\n|-\n|243\n| ''[[Jaalakam]]'' || Gopi Kurup\n|\n|-\n|244\n| ''[[Nadodikkattu]]'' || Balagopalan\n|\n|-\n|245\n| ''[[Oru Minnaminunginte Nurungu Vettam]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|246\n| ''[[Sarvakalashala]]'' || Innachan\n|\n|-\n|247\n| ''Ponnumkudathinu Pottu'' ||\n|\n|-\n|248\n| ''Ivide Ellavarkkum Sukham'' || Cheriyachen\n|\n|-\n|249\n| ''[[Unnikale Oru Kadha Parayam]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|250\n| ''Yagagni'' || Madhavan\n|\n|-\n|251\n| ''Itha Samayamayi'' ||\n|\n|-\n|252\n| [[Swathi Thirunal (film)|Swathi Thirunal]] || Krishna Ravu\n|\n|-\n|253\n|rowspan=\"34\"| 1986|| ''Ee Kaikalil'' || Ittoopp\n|\n|-\n|254\n| ''Nyayavidhi'' || Channar\n|\n|-\n|255\n| ''Rareeram'' || Lonappan\n|\n|-\n|256\n| ''Ayalvasi Oru Daridravasi'' || Kuttan Pillai\n|\n|-\n|257\n| ''[[Dheem Tharikida Thom]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|25