ne Puli'' || Saami\n|\n|-\n|297\n| ''Avidathepole Ivideyum'' ||\n|\n|-\n|298\n| ''Ambada Njaane'' || Kumaran\n|\n|-\n|299\n| ''Irakal'' ||\n|\n|-\n|300\n| ''Punnaaram Chollicholli'' ||\n|\n|-\n|301\n| ''[[Archana Aaradhana]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|302\n| ''[[Scene No. 7]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|303\n| ''Daivatheyorthu'' ||\n|\n|-\n|304\n|rowspan=\"3\"| 1984 || ''Koottinilamkili'' || Office Staff\n|\n|-\n|305\n| ''[[Paavam Poornima]]'' || Unnithan\n|\n|-\n|306\n| ''[[Panchavadi Palam]]'' || Barabas\n|\n|-\n|307\n|rowspan=\"4\"| 1983 || ''Prathijnja'' ||\n|\n|-\n|308\n| ''[[Mouna Raagam (1983 film)|Mouna Raagam]]'' || Freddy/Valyappan\n|\n|-\n|309\n| ''[[Prem Nazirine Kanmanilla]]'' || Film Producer\n|\n|-\n|310\n| ''[[Lekhayude Maranam Oru Flashback]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|311\n|rowspan=\"3\" | 1982|| ''Ilakkangal'' ||\n|\n|-\n|312\n| ''Ormaykkaay'' ||\n|\n|-\n|313\n| ''Idavela'' ||\n|\n|-\n|314\n|rowspan=\"1\"|1981|| ''Vida Parayum Munbe'' ||\n|\n|-\n|315\n|rowspan=\"1\" |1980 || ''Kochu Kochu Thettukal'' ||\n|\n|-\n|316\n|rowspan=\"1\"|1978 || ''[[Randu Penkuttikal]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|317\n|rowspan=\"1\" |1974|| ''Nellu'' ||\n|\n|-\n|318\n|rowspan=\"3\" |1973 || ''[[Jesus (1973 film)]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|319\n| ''[[Urvashi Bharathi]]'' ||\n|\n|-\n|320\n| ''Football Champion'' <ref>[http://www.mangalam.com/cinema/latest-news/215570] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809195737/http://www.mangalam.com/cinema/latest-news/215570 |date=9 August 2014 }}</ref>||\n|\n|-\n|321\n|rowspan=\"1\" |1972 || ''[[Nrithasala]]'' ||\n|\n|}\n\n;Other language films\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Title !! Role !! Language\n|-\n| 1998 || ''[[Doli Saja Ke Rakhna]]'' || Colonel Vincent|| [[Hindi]]\n|-\n| 2003 || ''[[Lesa Lesa]]'' || || [[Tamil language|Tamil]]\n|-\n| 2004 || ''[[Nothing But Life]]'' || Prof. Ponnachan PhD || English\n|-\n| 2006 || ''[[Malamaal Weekly]]'' || Anthony || Hindi\n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[Shikari (2012 film)|Shikari]]'' || Sitharam Setu || [[Kannada]]\n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Naan Avalai Sandhitha Pothu]]'' || || Tamil\n|}\n\n===Story===\n* ''Pavam IA Ivachan'' (1994)\n* ''Keerthanam'' (1995)\n\n===Producer===\n* ''Vida Parayum Munpe'' (1981)\n* ''Ilakkangal'' (1982)\n* ''Ormakkayi'' (1982)\n* ''Lekhayude Maranam Oru Flashback'' (1983)\n\n===Playback singing===\n* ''Aanachandam'' \u2013 Gajakesariyogam (1990)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.msidb.org/songs.php?tag%3DSearch%26singers%3DInnocent%26limit%3D5 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2015-04-24 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075253/http://en.msidb.org/songs.php?tag=Search&singers=Innocent&limit=5 |archivedate=4 March 2016 |df=dmy }}</ref>\n* ''Kandallo'' \u2013 Sandram (1990)\n* ''Kunukupenmaniye'' \u2013 Mr Butler (2000)\n* ''Onnam Malakeri'' \u2013 Kalyanaraman (2002)\n* ''Sundarakeralam'' \u2013 Doctor Innocentanu (2012)\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#ccc; text-align:center;\"\n! Year !! Title !! Role !! Channel\n|-\n|2020||[[Kudumbavilakku]]||Himself||Asianet\n|-\n|2019\u2013present||Comedy star season 2||Judge||Asianet\n|-\n|2019||Utsavam Super Star||Mentor||Flowers TV\n|-\n|2018||[[Top Singer (TV series)|Top Singer]]||Guest||[[Flowers (TV channel)|Flowers TV]]\n|-\n|2018||Nakshatra thilakkam||Guest||[[Mazhavil Manorama]]\n|-\n|2018||Chaya Koppa yile kodum kattu||himself||Mazhavil Manorama\n|-\n|2017||Comedy super night 2||guest||Flowers TV\n|-\n|2017||Star Chat||Guest|| WE TV\n|-\n|2016||J B junction||Guest||Kairali TV\n|-\n|2016||[[Badai Bungalow]]||Guest||[[Asianet (TV channel)|Asianet]]\n|-\n|2016||Comedy Carnival||himself||[[Mazhavil Manorama]]\n|-\n|2013||Point blank||Guest||Asianet News\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==Further reading==\n* {{Cite book| title=Cancer Wardile Chiri | publisher=Mathrubhui Books | date=12 December 2013 | author=Innocent | page=127 | isbn=9788182661110| id= {{ASIN|8182659108|country=in}} }}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Innocent (actor)}}\n* {{IMDb name|id=0409204|na