 (2004 film)|Employee of the Month]]''\n| Reverend Ben Goodwin\n|\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[Come Away Home]]''\n| Grandpa Donald Brooks\n|\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[Madison (film)|Madison]]''\n| Mayor Don Vaughn\n| \n|-\n| 2006\n| ''[[Cars (film)|Cars]]''\n| Sarge\n| Voice\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''[[For Your Consideration (film)|For Your Consideration]]''\n| Paper Badge Sergeant\n|\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Hairspray (2007 film)|Hairspray]]''\n| Mr. Spritzer\n|\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[Sunshine Cleaning]]''\n| Sherm\n|\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''Chronic Town''\n| Eleanor's Father\n|\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[Bedtime Stories (film)|Bedtime Stories]]''\n| Hot Dog Vendor\n|\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''[[Horsemen (film)|Horsemen]]''\n| Father Whiteleather\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''Ironmen''\n| Connors\n| \n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Thanks (film)|Thanks]]''\n| Hank\n| \n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Cars 2]]''\n| Sarge\n| Voice\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''Game Night''\n| Marvin Garden\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Turbo (film)|Turbo]]''\n| The Foreman\n| Voice\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Other People (film)|Other People]]''\n| Ronnie\n|\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''The Holy Man''\n| Lou 'The Bull' Devine\n|\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Cars 3]]''\n| Sarge\n| Voice\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class = \"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class = \"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 1963\n|''[[East Side/West Side]]''\n| Charlie Welty\n| Episode: \"No Hiding Place\"\n|-\n| 1964\n|''[[The Defenders (1961 TV series)|The Defenders]]''\n| R.W. Wheeler\n| Episode: \"Conflict of Interests\"\n|-\n| 1966\n|''[[Get Smart]]''\n| Hanlon\n| Episode: \"The Greatest Spy on Earth\"\n|-\n| 1966\n|''[[Bewitched]]''\n| TV Man\n| Episode: \"Oedipus Hex\"\n|-\n| 1968\n|''A Punt, a Pass, and a Prayer''\n| Photographer\n| Television film\n|-\n| 1970\n|''[[The Night the Animals Talked]]''\n|\n| Voice, Television special\n|-\n| 1972\n|''[[The Corner Bar]]''\n| Unknown character\n| Episode: \"Flanagan's Wake\"\n|-\n| 1974\u20131975\n|''[[Sesame Street]]''\n| Parrot\n| Voice, 2 episodes\n|-\n| 1977\n|''Simple Gifts''\n|\n| Vo